Titolo: Mario vs. Donkey Kong 2: March of the Minis

Anno: 2006

Descrizione: Mario vs. Donkey Kong 2: March of the Minis is the sequel to the Game Boy Advance game Mario vs. Donkey Kong released in 2006, a follow up to the Game Boy Donkey Kong game, though it is more puzzle-oriented, now that the player controls several Mini Marios with the touch screen instead of Mario himself. The game also features the return of Pauline, whose last appearance was in the 1994 Donkey Kong game, a Game Boy remake of the original Donkey Kong.  It features Nintendo Wi-Fi Connection.  The DS Download Station Series 3 set of games features a short demo of the game. This is the sixth Mario game for the Nintendo DS. A sequel, called Mario vs. Donkey Kong: Minis March Again!, was released in June 2009; it is available for download via the DSiWare service for 800 Nintendo Points.
On October 6, 2016, the game was released on the Wii U eShop under the virtual console branding.

